    "title": "B站各账号内容表现对比",
    "description": "B站5个账号的平均播放量、点赞数和评论数对比，可以看出AI破局者在播放量和互动数据上表现最佳，大山老师讲Ai相对较弱。",
    "querySql": "SELECT a.account_name, \n       ROUND(AVG(cms.views)) as avg_views,\n       ROUND(AVG(cms.likes)) as avg_likes,\n       ROUND(AVG(cms.comments)) as avg_comments\nFROM bilibili_accounts a\nJOIN contents c ON a.account_id = c.account_id\nLEFT JOIN content_metric_snapshots cms ON c.content_id = cms.content_id\nWHERE c.platform = 'bilibili'\nGROUP BY a.account_name\nORDER BY avg_views DESC NULLS LAST",
